estol inc was formed after three us postal contracts were acquired from burton hoovestol shortly thereafter hoovestol inc branched off into the refrigerated truckload and ltl businesses throughout the s hoovestol inc carried freight as well as mail across the country toward the end of that decade the freight side of the business was sold and hoovestol again became solely a mail contractor for the postal service to this day hauling mail for the postal service is the cornerstone of hoovestol inc although our main office and maintenance facility is located in eagan mn we also have shops in nebraska kansas illinois and massachusetts in addition we have service trucks located in seattle wa los angeles ca and jersey city nj all of our trucks and trailers are maintained at these facilities at hoovestol we pride ourselves on having some of the best and most loyal drivers in the trucking industry a typical day for a hoovestol driver is  to  hours long with only an occasional layover run our drivers are often scheduled out months in advance this allows for plenty of quality time with family and friends we are currently operating routes that run coast to coast and we hire drivers at designated locations along the way if you are interested in joining our company please visit the recruiting section of this website thank you and if i can be of assistance to you please feel free to contact me sincerelywayne hoovestol  hourly pay receive a competitive hourly rate plus health and welfare benefits we take care of our drivers priorities we do our best to keep drivers with their families reduce layovers and keep our equipment in top condition respect we treat our drivers fair and we do our best to exceed your expectations the only hitch is once you work for hoovestol you wont want to work for anyone else available positions click on a location for more details return to us view return to the map apply online release signing printable documents questions or concerns contact us by phone 